text:
Photo: Marvin Pfeiffer, Image 1 of / 1 1 East Central's Julie Kosub (1283) leaves the starting line of the Varsity girls 3-mile run in the Southwest ISD Invitational cross country meet at Southwest High School on Saturday, Aug. 29, 2015. Kosub finished third in the event with a time of 19 minutes, 0.55 seconds. MARVIN PFEIFFER/ mpfeiffer@express-news.net
